      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "# Svcregistry — Quick Reference\n\n## Endpoints (helixon-platform/cmd/svcregistryd)\n- `GET  /healthz`             — liveness\n- `GET  /metrics`             — Prometheus scrape (this dashboard)\n- `GET  /api/v1/services`     — JSON snapshot\n- `POST /api/v1/services`     — register (rejects port conflicts with 409)\n- `GET  /api/v1/conflicts`    — port-collision report\n\n## Counter semantics\n`svcregistry_operations_total{op=register|unregister|list|conflict,status=ok|error}`\n\n## Persistence\nSnapshot written atomically to `~/.config/svc-registry.json`. Crash-mid-write\nyields the previous snapshot (write-temp + rename).\n\n## Run\n`svcregistryd --addr :9103 --path ~/.config/svc-registry.json`\n",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.0",
      "title": "Operator notes",
      "type": "text"
    }
